      "rationale": "Experimental validation data obtained from FDA benchmark study using identical pump geometry, working fluid (bovine blood at 37°C, hematocrit 35%), and operating conditions. Test conditions documented with calibrated instrumentation. Flow rates measured with Coriolis meter (±0.5%), rotational speed with optical tachometer (±10 RPM). Temperature controlled to ±0.5°C.",
